bcnProducts.name: bcnProducts
bcnProducts.description: bcnProducts is the root for the OID values defined in BCN-PRODUCTS-MIB. Products might include hardware and/or software.

bcnMgmt.name: bcnMgmt
bcnMgmt.description: bcnSystems is the main subtree for new MIBs.

bcnServices.name: bcnServices
bcnServices.description: bcnServices is the root for the OID values defined in BCN-SERVICES-MIB. The intention is that the set of services define the type of system.

bcnModules.name: bcnModules
bcnModules.description: bcnModules provides a root object identifier from which MODULE-IDENTITY values may be assigned.

bcnExperimental.name: bcnExperimental
bcnExperimental.description: The bcnExperimental branch is intended for work in progress mibs. Objects in this part of the tree will be deleted when the work is complete and moved to its permanent location.
